title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 17 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Nov 17 2021
description:
Southern border chaos continues in October with record-setting arrests. DHS Secretary Mayorkas grades Biden immigration policy as "A For Effort." Open borders is the goal of the Democrat party. US overdose deaths break records. Why is the DOJ targeting parents as domestic terrorists? Former Education Secretary, Betsy DeVos, discussed with Clay and Buck the DOJ tracking parents and why education transparency is crucial for future generations. School choice and education freedom should be an imperative. Can anyone understand what Biden is saying?
